- Use, copy, share, and adapt this dataset for personal, research, educational, and other non-commercial purposes.
- Build non-commercial prompt tools, experiments, demos, and image-generation workflows based on this dataset.

## You may not

- Use this dataset for commercial purposes.
- Sell, resell, sublicense, or package this dataset as part of a paid product or paid service.
